<h1>Exceptions for operating hours</h1>
<p>Use this window to manage exceptions to regular intervals of modified <a href="../../../../../../alvao-service-desk/implementation/services/operating-hours">operating hours</a>.</p>

<p>Options:</p>
	<ul>
 <li><strong>Command Panel</strong><ul>
  <li><strong>New Exception</strong> - create <a href="exception-operating-hours">new exception</a>.</li>
  <li><strong>Edit</strong> - <a href="exception-operating-hours">edit</a> the selected exception.</li>
  <li><strong>Delete</strong> - remove the selected exception.</li>
  </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>Exception Table</strong>- contains the exceptions. You can <a href="../../../../../../alvao-asset-management/working-with-tables">customize</a> the table as needed.</li>
	</ul>





</asp:Content>
